{
  "number": 83,
  "name": "سُورَةُ المُطَفِّفِينَ",
  "englishName": "Al-Mutaffifin",
  "englishNameTranslation": "Defrauding",
  "revelationType": "Meccan",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 5849,
      "text": "WOE UNTO THOSE who give short measure:",
      "numberInSurah": 1,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5850,
      "text": "those who, when they are to receive their due from [other] people, demand that it be given in full –",
      "numberInSurah": 2,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5851,
      "text": "but when they have to measure or weigh whatever they owe to others, give less than what is due!",
      "numberInSurah": 3,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5852,
      "text": "Do they not know that they are bound to be raised from the dead",
      "numberInSurah": 4,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5853,
      "text": "[and called to account] on an awesome Day –",
      "numberInSurah": 5,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5854,
      "text": "the Day when all men shall stand before the Sustainer of all the worlds?",
      "numberInSurah": 6,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 587,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5855,
      "text": "NAY, VERILY, the record of the wicked is indeed [set down] in a mode inescapable!",
      "numberInSurah": 7,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5856,
      "text": "And what could make thee conceive what that that mode inescapable will be?",
      "numberInSurah": 8,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5857,
      "text": "A record [indelibly] inscribed!",
      "numberInSurah": 9,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5858,
      "text": "Woe on that Day unto those who give the lie to the truth –",
      "numberInSurah": 10,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5859,
      "text": "those who give the lie to the [coming of] Judgment Day:",
      "numberInSurah": 11,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5860,
      "text": "for, none gives the lie to it but such as are wont to transgress against all that is [and are] immersed in sin:",
      "numberInSurah": 12,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5861,
      "text": "[and so,] whenever Our messages are conveyed to them, they but say, \"Fables of ancient times!\"",
      "numberInSurah": 13,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5862,
      "text": "Nay, but their hearts are corroded by all [the evil] that they were wont to do!",
      "numberInSurah": 14,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5863,
      "text": "Nay, verily, from [the grace of] their Sustainer shall they on that Day be debarred;",
      "numberInSurah": 15,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5864,
      "text": "and then, behold, they shall enter the blazing fire",
      "numberInSurah": 16,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5865,
      "text": "and be told: \"This is the [very thing] to which you were wont to give the lie!\"",
      "numberInSurah": 17,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5866,
      "text": "NAY, VERILY - the record of the truly virtuous is [set down] in a mode most lofty!",
      "numberInSurah": 18,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5867,
      "text": "And what could make thee conceive what that mode most lofty will be?",
      "numberInSurah": 19,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5868,
      "text": "A record [indelibly] inscribed,",
      "numberInSurah": 20,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5869,
      "text": "witnessed~ by all who have [ever] been drawn close unto God.",
      "numberInSurah": 21,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5870,
      "text": "Behold, [in the life to come] the truly virtuous will indeed be in bliss:",
      "numberInSurah": 22,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5871,
      "text": "[resting on couches, they will look up [to God]:",
      "numberInSurah": 23,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5872,
      "text": "upon their faces thou wilt see the brightness of bliss.",
      "numberInSurah": 24,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5873,
      "text": "They will be given a drink of pure wine whereon the seal [of God] will have been set,",
      "numberInSurah": 25,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5874,
      "text": "pouring forth with a fragrance of musk. To that [wine of paradise], then, let all such aspire as [are willing to] aspire to things of high account:",
      "numberInSurah": 26,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5875,
      "text": "for it is composed of all that is most exalting",
      "numberInSurah": 27,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5876,
      "text": "a source [of bliss] whereof those who are drawn close unto God shall drink.",
      "numberInSurah": 28,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5877,
      "text": "BEHOLD, those who have abandoned themselves to sin are wont to laugh at such as have attained to faith",
      "numberInSurah": 29,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5878,
      "text": "and whenever they pass by them, they wink at one another [derisively];",
      "numberInSurah": 30,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5879,
      "text": "and whenever they return to people of their own kind, they return full of jests;",
      "numberInSurah": 31,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5880,
      "text": "and whenever they see those [who believe,] they say, \"Behold, these [people] have indeed gone astray!\"",
      "numberInSurah": 32,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5881,
      "text": "And, withal, they have no call to watch over [the beliefs of] others...",
      "numberInSurah": 33,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5882,
      "text": "But on the Day [of Judgment], they who had attained to faith will [be able to] laugh at the [erstwhile] deniers of the truth:",
      "numberInSurah": 34,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 588,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5883,
      "text": "[for, resting in paradise] on couches, they will look on [and say to themselves]:",
      "numberInSurah": 35,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 589,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5884,
      "text": "\"Are these deniers of the truth being [thus] requited for [aught but] what they were wont to do?\"",
      "numberInSurah": 36,
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 589,
      "ruku": 525,
      "hizbQuarter": 235,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ],
